{"tid":967001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行山客墮五米崖重創","createTime":"2019-01-03T08:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T13:42:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"383e21ef8935227208e88b124020fc2b739336ef","tid":967001,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:00:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190103/20582642\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190103%2F20582642&d=0uxXn7C%2FpHl%2FswxxB4gUXwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=852fd53b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190103%2F20582642&h=56b25098\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190103/20582642</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月03日 <br />\n<br />\n行山客墮五米崖重創<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190103/large/0102leungckdsc03875.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190103%2Flarge%2F0102leungckdsc03875.jpg&h=8bf7c0c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飛行服務隊直升機到場搜救墮崖男子。梁澤岡攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名行山客昨晨與友人在西貢遠足時，失足墮下五米深的山崖，撼傷頭及腳部陷半昏迷，同行友人報警。救援人員兵分兩路上山拯救，傷者最終由政府飛行服務隊救起轉送醫院，搶救後情況嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直升機救起送院<br />\n<br />\n墮崖男子姓鄭（58歲），頭部受傷及腳部骨折，意外後一度陷入半昏迷，政府飛行服務隊直升機將事主救起，送往大嶼山飛行服務隊總部，再由救護車送至北大嶼山醫院，經初步治理後轉至瑪嘉烈醫院，情況嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n現場為麥理浩徑第三段仙人河石一帶，沿途佈滿碎石，山勢險要。據悉，事主一行五男三女，昨晨約9時由西貢沙角尾出發，大約三小時後行至上址時，突然失足墮下約五米深山崖，同行友人報警。由於現場遠離車路，救援人員分別由馬鞍山郊野公園及西貢大水井登山，並召政府飛行服務隊直升機協助，約40分鐘後將傷者救起。<br />\n<br />\n麥理浩徑第三段是十段之中最難走的第二段，此段由北潭凹於海拔150米起步，先登上約400米的牛耳石山，然後再下降至300米的嶂上，往西南方向行，經過畫眉山及雷打石，返回起步的海拔150米，然後再攀升上400米高的雞公山，最後到達企嶺下，在西沙路完結。<br />\n<br />\n■記者簡明恩、梁澤岡  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n勾斗車輾斃過路院友<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n黑衣男蘋果大樓淋油"},{"pid":"5f07ba7cd082ddbf4ecbbaaeba356560b0fe715b","tid":967001,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"而家D老野 成日行高難度山打卡呃LIKE<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d5fc0acb83ead33feaba64ff486d42a6e13b0f","tid":967001,"uid":45082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f07ba7cd082ddbf4ecbbaaeba356560b0fe715b","tid":967001,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"而家D老野 成日行高難度山打卡呃LIKE<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:58:03.000Z","msg":"其實後生都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a252ffa5fd8577c1b0c467cf78de5b99799f02a","tid":967001,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:40:28.000Z","msg":"仙人跳"},{"pid":"afa78ce3d14ea35da73348bb97fdce2cf6527976","tid":967001,"uid":17481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a252ffa5fd8577c1b0c467cf78de5b99799f02a","tid":967001,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:40:28.000Z","msg":"仙人跳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:42:09.000Z","msg":"跳完做仙人"},{"pid":"ff59e1a692f62d96b3cfc7fae40cc01980e94a23","tid":967001,"uid":4806,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"麥理浩徑第三段是十段之中最難走的第二段<br />\n睇到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca296885c311d41ffac8e67f5d33eca02dccdcf6","tid":967001,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:47:56.000Z","msg":"行過一次，係少石屎路的一段，但唔難行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1c25d3104a68d50df1e78e1d809baee183b2a5","tid":967001,"uid":9466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff59e1a692f62d96b3cfc7fae40cc01980e94a23","tid":967001,"uid":4806,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime